OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782521274
OL,3,CForeign secretary threatens Israel
OL,4,Cwith further sanctions
OL,6,FThe foreign secretary has threatened
OL,7,FIsrael with further sanctions and said
OL,8,Fthat the government will need to "take
OL,9,Fstronger action" on the country amid
OL,10,Fan ongoing conflict in the Middle East.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News exclusively,
OL,13,FYvette Cooper said that she is "deeply
OL,14,Fworried about what is happening in
OL,15,FPalestine", adding that the government
OL,16,Fwill "have to do more".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
