PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782521274
OL,3,CForeign secretary threatens Israel
OL,4,Cwith further sanctions
OL,6,FThis comes at a time when conflict in
OL,7,FGaza and the West Bank is flaring up
OL,8,Fagain despite a ceasefire agreed
OL,9,Fbetween Israel and Hamas in October
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,FThe government is currently not
OL,13,Fannouncing any new policy while it
OL,14,Fawaits a new leader, with Andy Burnham
OL,15,Flooking like the most likely successor.
OL,17,FBurnham's soft-left approach to
OL,18,Fpolitics may mean that he supports
OL,19,FCooper's suggestion of stronger
OL,20,Fsanctions, but he has yet to announce
OL,21,Fhis foreign policy ideas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782521274
OL,3,CForeign secretary threatens Israel
OL,4,Cwith further sanctions
OL,6,FCooper is on a trip to Poland,
OL,7,Fvisiting a military training facility,
OL,8,Fwhen she told ITV News' Political
OL,9,FEditor Robert Peston that the
OL,10,Fgovernment is "looking at what further
OL,11,Fwe can do" to strengthen sanctions.
OL,13,FShe said: "We've seen in Gaza that the
OL,14,F20-point plan is currently stalled,
OL,15,Fand I am very worried about what's
OL,16,Fhappening there, but I'm also very
OL,17,Fworried about what is happening in the
OL,18,FWest Bank.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
