PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782521274
OL,3,CForeign secretary threatens Israel
OL,4,Cwith further sanctions
OL,6,F"We've seen increases in settler
OL,7,Fviolence and also the expansion of
OL,8,Fsettlements in a way that looks
OL,9,Fdesigned to prevent any possibility of
OL,10,Fa sustainable two-state solution, and
OL,11,Fyou have some people even just talking
OL,12,Fabout the most dangerous and damaging
OL,13,Fthings."
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
