PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782521274
OL,3,CForeign secretary threatens Israel
OL,4,Cwith further sanctions
OL,6,FThe foreign secretary was asked
OL,7,Fwhether Burnham, the potential new PM,
OL,8,Fwould be tougher on Israel after she
OL,9,Fpublicly backed him and said he is the
OL,10,F"right person" for the job.
OL,12,FBurnham is yet to confirm his stance
OL,13,Fon foreign policy, but is due to speak
OL,14,Fon Monday about his plans for the
OL,15,Feconomy and wider devolution.
OL,17,FSpeculation continues over who Burnham
OL,18,Fmay retain in his cabinet, with many
OL,19,Fsenior Labour figures coming out to
OL,20,Fback him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
